@nightly @moodle
Feature: Moodle.User Story 11609 - Forum Discussion Pin and Forum Discussion Unpin

  @IntegrationTest @EndToEndTest
  Scenario: TC Unpin a Forum Discussion for a Given Course
    Given Unpin a Forum Discussion for a Given Course
    When Forum Discussion Got successfully Unpinned for a Given Course
    Then Forum Discussion Unpinned Event should get generated and sent to our Raw Event Index
    And ['event'].['@context'] = 'http://purl.imsglobal.org/ctx/caliper/v1/Context'
    And ['event'].['@type'] = 'http://purl.imsglobal.org/caliper/v1/ForumEvent'
    And ['event'].['actor'].['@type'] = 'http://purl.imsglobal.org/caliper/v1/lis/Person'
    And ['event'].['action'] = 'http://purl.imsglobal.org/vocab/caliper/v1/action#Unpinned'
    And ['event'].['object'].['@type'] = 'http://purl.imsglobal.org/caliper/v1/AssignableDigitalResource'
    And ['event'].['object'].['extensions'].['moduleType'] = 'forum_discussions'
    And ['event'].['edApp'].['@type'] = 'http://purl.imsglobal.org/caliper/v1/SoftwareApplication'
    And ['event'].['edApp'].['name'] = 'IntellifyLearning'

